1.1 Give Us Your Feedback
If you experience any problems with the materials please use Polarion's documenting feature to provide your feedback. Just add a document review comment to the specific paragraph and send a round trip export to your sales or consultant. If you prefer you can also send an email to <a href="mailto:trainings@polarion.com">trainings@polarion.com</a>

